title: Suggestion to the New Version!
comment: Hi, Nilhcem!  Would you please consider to add the "Batch Replace" function to the new version?  Well, here I means, when the same IP (such as 8.7.6.5) pointed to multiple different hosts, and latter it need to be change to another IP (such as 5.6.7.8), the "Batch Replace" function would easier to do that work!

Thanks for the feature request, I will see if it can implemented easily. Otherwise, a workaround is to create only one entry with multiple hosts separated with a space, i.e. for 127.0.0.1: "localhost host1 host2.example.com host3.example org". This way you only need to edit one entry when the IP changes
